<h1>Privacy Policy — Infinite Fact</h1>
<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 24 February 2026</p>

<p>Infinite Fact (“we”, “our”, or “us”) is an educational mobile application designed for children to learn interesting facts in a fun and interactive way. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you use our application.</p>

<h2>1. Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
<p>Infinite Fact does not require users to create an account, log in, or provide personal information. We do not directly collect personal data such as name, email address, phone number, or location.</p>

<h2>2. Advertising</h2>
<p>Our app uses Google AdMob, a third-party advertising service, to display advertisements. AdMob may collect and use certain information automatically, including Advertising ID, device information, and interaction data with advertisements.</p>

<p>This information is used to provide and improve advertising services. We display child-appropriate advertisements in compliance with the Google Play Families Policy where applicable.</p>

<p>You can learn more about how Google uses data here:<br>
https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads</p>

<h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>The app may use third-party services that may collect information used to identify you. Third-party service providers used: Google AdMob (Advertising).</p>

<h2>4. Children’s Privacy</h2>
<p>Infinite Fact is designed for educational purposes and may be used by children. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

<h2>5. Data Security</h2>
<p>We value user privacy and take reasonable steps to protect information processed through third-party services.</p>

<h2>6. External Links</h2>
<p>The app may contain links to external websites (such as Privacy Policy or Terms pages). We are not responsible for the content or practices of those sites.</p>

<h2>7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>

<h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have any questions or suggestions about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at:<br>
Email: infoglpgustavo@gmail.com</p>

